Package ru.nsu.zhao

Class PrimeCheck

java.lang.Object
ru.nsu.zhao.PrimeCheck
public class PrimeCheck extends Object
质数检查工具类 Prime Check Utility Class 提供三种方法进行质数检查： Three methods are provided for prime number checking: 1. 顺序执行 Sequential Execution 2. 使用 parallelStream() 并行执行 Parallel Stream Execution 3. 使用多线程 (Threads) 并行执行 Multi-threaded Execution
